transcript:
How do you like this weather?
I don't like it, it's  too hot.
Mmhmm
But my kids like it. They like to go swimming.
Oh, where do they like to go swimming?

How are you doing today?
Not great, I didn't sleep much last night.
Aww...
I was working really late.
Are you working late again tonight?

How are you doing?
Not good, my arm hurts a lot.
I'm sorry to hear that.
Yeah, I fell last week.
Are you going to the doctor?

Do you have any plans for the weekend?
Yes! I'm moving to a new apartment.
That's awesome!
Yeah, I'm excited to move.
Where is your new apartment?

How's your day going?
Great, I got a new job!
Congratulations!
Thanks, I'm excited.
Where is your new job?

What did you do this weekend?
I went to a movie on Sunday.
Cool!
I saw the new Star Wars movie.
Did you like it?

How are your kids doing?
Great, my son got into college.
Wow!
I know, I'm really excited for him.
What college is he going to?

How is your week going?
Good, I went to Sacramento yesterday.
Oh, interesting!
I was visiting my aunt and uncle there.
What did you do together?

How is your family doing?
Great! My sister had her baby.
Aww!
Here's a photo. Isn't she cute?
Yes! What's her name?
